This </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">innovative design enables material to flow around the core pins, significantly reducing material usage and the need for secondary machining operations.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:15px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:15px;">  •  </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Tonnage Range:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> The LSP Series is available from 220 to 1600 tons, catering to a wide range of forging needs. letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Eccentric Dual Plunger Design:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> The EHW Series boasts a unique eccentric dual plunger mechanism that ensures direct force delivery to the workpiece. This design minimizes off-center loads, resulting in superior part quality and extended die life. The two plunger guides deliver tonnage vertically, unlike traditional crankshaft-style presses, which are prone to side thrust loads.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Tonnage Range:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> With a robust tonnage range from 330 to 2200 tons, the EHW Series is versatile enough to handle various applications, from intricate electronic components to large automotive parts.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>I-PRESS® Control System:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> At the heart of the EHW Series is the I-PRESS® control, the most advanced press and automation control available. Available on Rockwell AB, Siemens, and Omron platforms, I-PRESS® ensures seamless integration into any production environment.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Energy Efficiency:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> The EHW Series is engineered for optimal energy consumption. Available on Rockwell AB, Siemens, and Omron platforms, I-PRESS® ensures seamless integration into any production environment.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Energy Efficiency:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> The EHW Series is engineered for optimal energy consumption. letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Eccentric Dual Plunger Design:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> The EHW Series boasts a unique eccentric dual plunger mechanism that ensures direct force delivery to the workpiece. This design minimizes off-center loads, resulting in superior part quality and extended die life. The two plunger guides deliver tonnage vertically, unlike traditional crankshaft-style presses, which are prone to side thrust loads.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Tonnage Range:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> With a robust tonnage range from 330 to 2200 tons, the EHW Series is versatile enough to handle various applications, from intricate electronic components to large automotive parts.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>I-PRESS® Control System:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> At the heart of the EHW Series is the I-PRESS® control, the most advanced press and automation control available. Available on Rockwell AB, Siemens, and Omron platforms, I-PRESS® ensures seamless integration into any production environment.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Energy Efficiency:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> The EHW Series is engineered for optimal energy consumption. Available on Rockwell AB, Siemens, and Omron platforms, I-PRESS® ensures seamless integration into any production environment.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Energy Efficiency:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> The EHW Series is engineered for optimal energy consumption. letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Eccentric Dual Plunger Design:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> The EHW Series boasts a unique eccentric dual plunger mechanism that ensures direct force delivery to the workpiece. This design minimizes off-center loads, resulting in superior part quality and extended die life. The two plunger guides deliver tonnage vertically, unlike traditional crankshaft-style presses, which are prone to side thrust loads.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Tonnage Range:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> With a robust tonnage range from 330 to 2200 tons, the EHW Series is versatile enough to handle various applications, from intricate electronic components to large automotive parts.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>I-PRESS® Control System:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> At the heart of the EHW Series is the I-PRESS® control, the most advanced press and automation control available. Available on Rockwell AB, Siemens, and Omron platforms, I-PRESS® ensures seamless integration into any production environment.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">  • </SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><U>Energy Efficiency:</U></SPAN><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"> The EHW Series is engineered for optimal energy consumption. The I-PRESS® also enables real-time monitoring of critical parameters such as oil temperature, flow rates, and valve positions, ensuring your press operates within the desired parameters for maximum productivity.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><B>Applications and Versatility:</B></SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">The HP1 is not just a press; it’s a solution to many forming challenges. The I-PRESS® also enables real-time monitoring of critical parameters such as oil temperature, flow rates, and valve positions, ensuring your press operates within the desired parameters for maximum productivity.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><B>Applications and Versatility:</B></SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">The HP1 is not just a press; it’s a solution to many forming challenges. The forge industry benefits from the HP1’s ability to deliver controlled force for precisely shaping and forming metal parts.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';"><B>Energy Efficiency and Safety:</B></SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-family:'Calibri';"/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri';">Energy efficiency is a hallmark of the HP1, with servo-driven hydraulics that can result in significant energy savings compared to traditional hydraulic presses. Central to the press's design is its crankshaft mechanism, which offers exceptional mechanical leverage and efficiency. The I-PRESS® control ensures seamless integration with your existing automation, including feeders, robots, and transfer systems, making it a versatile solution for any press room.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;">The SP2 series, with its robust medium-sized frame, is engineered for consistent, high-speed performance while maintaining the highest quality standards. Central to the press's design is its crankshaft mechanism, which offers exceptional mechanical leverage and efficiency. This design ensures superior slide motion control and precision, guaranteeing optimal alignment and repeatability with every stroke. The I-PRESS® control ensures seamless integration with your existing automation, including feeders, robots, and transfer systems, making it a versatile solution for any press room.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;">The SP2 series, with its robust medium-sized frame, is engineered for consistent, high-speed performance while maintaining the highest quality standards. The I-PRESS® control ensures seamless integration with your existing automation, including feeders, robots, and transfer systems, making it a versatile solution for any press room.</SPAN></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN/></SPAN></DIV><DIV STYLE="text-align:left;font-size:14px;"><SPAN STYLE="display:inline-block; letter-spacing:0px; white-space:pre-wrap;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size:14px;">The SP2 series, with its robust medium-sized frame, is engineered for consistent, high-speed performance while maintaining the highest quality standards.
